data.description:
Excellent Opportunity for investors and owner occupants willing and financially able to invest sweat equity into this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, brick home with approximately 3,725 sqf and located in the village of Edmore. 

Main level features living area open to the kitchen with fireplace in breakfast nook, formal dining area, all bedrooms and bathrooms. Lower level features large family room with fireplace, laundry and plenty of space for storage. 
 
Additional amenities: 3 car garage, plus large shed, large covered back porch with an outdoor fireplace, 0.8 acre which provides plenty of space for personal enjoyment.
 
All public utilities including natural gas and access to cable television with high speed internet. 

Cash and Conventional loan financing ONLY.
